Sequence/Results Flag

Code Description Comment Version
C Cyclical Used for indicating a repeating cycle of service requests; for example, individual intravenous solutions used in a cyclical sequence (a.k.a. "Alternating IVs"). This value would be compatible with linking separate service requests or with having all cycli added v2.5

S Sequential added v2.5
